node.text:
Well. If you would like, Rofwufufuf, ey would 'ave you fer as long as you'd wish to ssstay.

{{emote|*Rofwufufuf snarls and runs on all fours to the great dragon. He immediately nips and licks Azhdahak's scaled ankles. Azhdahak growls and exhales a puff of ethanol from his nostrils.*}}

Thanksss, =name=. Ye have my eternal gratitude.

start.text:
ah, ehehe. hi =name=.~
azhdak is very strong. very warm.~
ehehe, like see you! {{emote|*He tries to lick your face. You let him.*}}

wat you want? rofuf want no fite right now.~
go. {{emote|*scritch, scritch*}} ruf want no fite.~
{{emote|*scritch scritch. It's ignoring you.*}}

node.text:
ehehehe, rofuf happy. like azhdak.

{{emote|*He drops on all fours and gnaws a weapon hilt from his belt, dropping it on the floor. He nudges it toward you with his nose.*}}

take this. ehehe. made this for you.
